290005         OF ATTRIBUTE EXCEPTIONTASK OF MYSELF TO LINKTOCOMS.
290006      CHANGE ATTRIBUTE TITLE OF "DCILIBRARY" TO LINKTOCOMS.
290007      ENABLE INPUT COMS-IN KEY "ONLINE".
