853700*
853800*
853900*
854000*    FIND    LAST    VISTORIASE2     AT
854100*            VIS-CHASSI              =       PLC-CHASSIS
854200*      ON    EXCEPTION
854300*       IF   DMSTATUS (NOTFOUND)
854400*            MOVE    "N"             TO      CH-LAUDO
854500*       ELSE
854600*            DISPLAY "PC/GAA/T640/DB: FIND ERROR LAST VISTORIASE2"
854650*            PERFORM 9000-E-ERRODB   THRU    9000-S-ERRODB
